A '''resistance''' on [[Chandrila/Legends|Chandrila]] was an anti-[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] resistance movement led by [[Mon Mothma/Legends|Mon Mothma]] on Chandrila during the early [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]]. It later became one of the founding members of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]].

